    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Okay, that makes sense. It sounds pretty risky though. Are there specific things I should look out for in the rest of the contract that might hide extra liability like that? Like, are there certain words or sneaky ways they can expand this beyond just my direct mistakes?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
