      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Be vigilant for overly broad language like \"any and all claims\" or carve-outs that place liability on you for the Disclosing Party's own mistakes. Specifically, review the \"Representations and Warranties\" section to see what you are guaranteeing about the information provided. Always look for exceptions or limitations to liability clauses elsewhere to ensure the indemnification isn't unlimited.",
